title: Ep160: Boundaries & Virtual Sex Orgies Feat Miss Cory B

description:
The Corona Virus isn't stopping this show! This week we are joined by sex educator, kink coach and 1/2 of the Never Have I Ever Podcast, Miss Cory B! We catch up on how covid-19 is affecting our day to day lives before playing a game of Never Have I Ever and then sharing the things we have done sexually and will NEVER do again! This is followed up by discussing boundaries and unwanted sex acts during consensual sex before the WD leads us into our journeys navigating sex. Cory shares her introduction to the sex world and Mandii & Weezy both share what has changed for them in understanding sex since the inception of the show. Enjoyed this week's episode? Let us know by tweeting us @whoreiblepod or using the hashtag #Whoreibledecisions. Also follow along and comment on @Whoreible_decisions on IG Keep up with this week's guest everywhere!
